content:
There are no enemy ships in the Black Sea water area, there are 1 enemy ship in the Azov Sea, 3 enemy ships in the Mediterranean.

This was reported in the morning of March 8 by the Navy forces of the Armed Forces.

According to them, among the enemy ships in the Mediterranean there are 1 carrier of winged missiles "Caliber" with a total volley of up to 4 missiles.

During the day, in the interests of the Russian Federation, the passage of the Kerch Strait was made:

6 vessels to the Azov Sea, 1 of them moved from the Bosphorus Strait;

There are 6 vessels to the Black Sea, no one continued to move in the direction of the Bosphorus.

The Russian Federation continues to violate the International Convention on the Protection of Human Life at the Sea of 1974 (Solas), switching off automatic identification systems (AIS).

Earlier in the Navy of the Armed ForcespredictedA new goal for destruction in the Russian Navy.
